751
00:43:52,672 --> 00:43:54,382
- Komandan Pos Terdepan.
- Ya?

752
00:43:55,466 --> 00:43:56,884
Ini tentang Kang Seong-jae.

753
00:43:56,968 --> 00:43:57,969
Bisakah kamu...

754
